info.author: Randy Syring
info.description:
Introduction
---------------

BlazeGrid (formerly pysdatagrid) is designed to generate HTML tables from static
or dynamic data resources.

Questions & Comments
---------------------

Please visit: http://groups.google.com/group/blazelibs

Current Status
---------------

Current code has a good bit of testing, but API changes very likely.

The `BlazeGrid tip <http://bitbucket.org/rsyring/blazegrid/get/tip.zip#egg=blazegrid-dev>`_
is installable via `easy_install` with ``easy_install BlazeGrid==dev``.
